snippet.title: Cozy Grove: Camp Spirit | Pre-Reg Trailer | Netflix
snippet.description:
Help ghostly bears find peace in this relaxing sequel to the beloved
role-playing game where kindness rules and new friends, crafts and
mysteries await.

Play Cozy Grove: Camp Spirit on your mobile devices. Available
exclusively on Netflix: https://bit.ly/cozygrovecampspirit

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services, with 270 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.
